    <div id="section2">
            <h1>登入</h1>
            <hr>
            <p> 接口名称：<code>login</code><br/>
                接口说明：调用登入页面进行登入。 <br/>
                HTTP Method : <code>GET</code><br/>
                范例：<pre><code class="js">http://gameapi.smartgamesltd.com/login</code></pre>

                <div class="well well-sm">
                    <img src=<%= "assets/img/" + lang + "/pic07.png"%> class="img-responsive"/>
                </div>

                调用回传页面的 JavaScript 函式 <code>GetResult()</code> 来取得回传结果。该函式回传 JSON 字串，例如<code>{"code": 1, "msg": "ok"}</code>。 <br/>
                <a href="/webapi-init#section5"> 查看回传值定义 </a>
            </p>

            <table class="table table-striped"> <!--Gem Start-->
                <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>
                        变数
                    </th>
                    <th>
                        详细说明
                    </th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Code
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        code = 201 为成功，其他都是失败。
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td>
                        OpenID
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        登入帐号的 SG 平台识别 ID，登入成功后以此 ID 登入游戏伺服器。
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td>
                        SessionID
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        连线的 SessionID，用以登入二次验证。
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Token
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        成功登入后可以此 Token 向渠道 Server 取得帐号资料。
                    </td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
