    <div id="section10">
        <h1>Session ID 登入验证</h1>
        <hr>
        <p>
            接口名称：<code>verifysession</code><br/>
            接口说明：使用 SessionID 取得登入帐号资讯。
            参数列表： <br/>
        </p>
        <table class="table table-striped"> <!--Gem Start-->
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>
                    参数名称
                </th>
                <th>
                    参数说明
                </th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    appId
                </td>
                <td>
                    开发者申请开通游戏后取得的gamekey。例如 d7e73390-d7fd-11e6-9074-21c247f06802
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class>
                <td>
                    session
                </td>
                <td>
                    登入成功后取得的 sessionID。
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    uid
                </td>
                <td>
                    登入成功后取得的openid。
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    signature
                </td>
                <td>
                    登入成功后回传的sign。
                </td>
            </tr>

            </tbody>
        </table>
        <p>
            HTTP Method : <code>GET</code><br/>
            范例：<pre><code class="js">http://gameapi.smartgamesltd.com/verifysession?appId=d7e73390-d7fd-11e6-9074-21c247f06802&session=xxxx&uid=10000000&signature=xxxx</code></pre>
            返回值：回传 JSON 字串。 <br/>
            例如<code>{"Account" : "abc@gmail.com", "OpenID" : 1000000000, "EMail" : "abc@gmail.com"}</code>。 <br/>
        </p>
    </div>
    <br/>
    <div id="section11">
        <h1>Token 登入验证</h1>
        <hr>
        <p>
            接口名称：<code>verifytoken</code><br/>
            接口说明：使用 Token 取得登入帐号资讯。 <br/>
            参数：token（登入成功后取得）<br/>
            HTTP Method : <code>GET</code><br/>
            范例：<pre><code class="js">http://gameapi.smartgamesltd.com/verifytoken?token=xxxxx</code></pre>
            返回值：回传 JSON 字串。 <br/>
            例如<code>{"Account" : "abc@gmail.com", "OpenID" : 1000000000, "EMail" : "abc@gmail.com"}</code>。 <br/>
        </p>
    </div>
